  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Lord Evans' statement on the resignation of Sir Alex Allan KCB
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Lord Evans responds to the resignation of the Prime Minister's Independent Adviser on Ministers' Interests, Sir Alex Allan</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
